reviewText: First class production and very moving Thankyou very much for producing this DVD

I love this series of documentaries by Tim Keesee. But I love even more that God is powerfully at work to spread His Word in places where the gospel has not been heard. This 7th DVD is my favorite. God's light shines the brightest in the darkest circumstances. I am thankful for men and women of God who are unafraid to spread the gospel at the risk of their own safety.
Brilliant retelling of what God is doing amongst the nations. Bringing His Gospel to the ends of the earth.
Well written and well produced. The quality of filming is outstanding. The stories of faith are even better. The gospel is triumphing!

These documentaries help focus your prayer for missionaries and the church movements in particular parts of the world by alerting you with first hand knowledge of the trials men and women of God face around the world. They also give you great encouragement that Jesus is active and still seeking and calling His own, even in some of the most trying circumstances!
